  "flavor_text_entries": [
    {
      "flavor_text": "体の　中では　血液の　かわりに\n必要な　栄養と　酸素を　運ぶために\n灼熱の　マグマが　循環している。",
      "language": {
        "name": "ja",
        "url": "json/language/0011.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "alpha-sapphire",
        "url": "json/version/0026.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Slugma does not have any blood in its body. Instead, intensely\nhot magma circulates throughout this Pokémon’s body,\ncarrying essential nutrients and oxygen to its organs.",
      "language": {
        "name": "en",
        "url": "json/language/0009.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "alpha-sapphire",
        "url": "json/version/0026.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Nel corpo di Slugma non scorre nemmeno una goccia di\nsangue, bensì magma rovente, che garantisce l’apporto di\nossigeno e sostanze nutritive fondamentali per i suoi organi.",
      "language": {
        "name": "it",
        "url": "json/language/0008.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "alpha-sapphire",
        "url": "json/version/0026.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Slugma no tiene sangre en su organismo, sino ardiente\nmagma que hace circular por todo el cuerpo los nutrientes\ny el oxígeno que necesitan sus órganos.",
      "language": {
        "name": "es",
        "url": "json/language/0007.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "alpha-sapphire",
        "url": "json/version/0026.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Schneckmag hat kein Blut in seinem Körper. Stattdessen fließt\nglühend heißes Magma in diesem Pokémon, das seine Organe\nmit lebenswichtigen Nährstoffen und Sauerstoff versorgt.",
      "language": {
        "name": "de",
        "url": "json/language/0006.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "alpha-sapphire",
        "url": "json/version/0026.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Les veines de Limagma ne contiennent pas de sang.\nAu lieu de ça, du magma en fusion circule dans le corps\nde ce Pokémon, apportant les nutriments et l’oxygène\nnécessaires à ses organes.",
      "language": {
        "name": "fr",
        "url": "json/language/0005.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "alpha-sapphire",
        "url": "json/version/0026.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "몸 안에는 혈액 대신\n필요한 영양과 산소를 운반하기 위해\n작열하는 마그마가 순환되고 있다.",
      "language": {
        "name": "ko",
        "url": "json/language/0003.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "alpha-sapphire",
        "url": "json/version/0026.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "からだの　なかでは　けつえきの　かわりに\nひつような　えいようと　さんそを　はこぶために\nしゃくねつの　マグマが　じゅんかんしている。",
      "language": {
        "name": "ja-Hrkt",
        "url": "json/language/0001.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "alpha-sapphire",
        "url": "json/version/0026.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "体の　中では　灼熱の　溶岩が\n渦巻いているが　冷えると　固まって　しまい\n崩れて　体が　小さく　なっていく。",
      "language": {
        "name": "ja",
        "url": "json/language/0011.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "omega-ruby",
        "url": "json/version/0025.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Molten magma courses throughout Slugma’s circulatory\nsystem. If this Pokémon is chilled, the magma cools and\nhardens. Its body turns brittle and chunks fall off, reducing\nits size.",
      "language": {
        "name": "en",
        "url": "json/language/0009.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "omega-ruby",
        "url": "json/version/0025.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Nel corpo di Slugma scorre magma liquido. In caso di\ncongelamento, il magma si raffredda e si solidifica. Il corpo\ndiventa fragile e cade a pezzi consumandosi progressivamente.",
      "language": {
        "name": "it",
        "url": "json/language/0008.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "omega-ruby",
        "url": "json/version/0025.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Por el sistema circulatorio de Slugma corre magma líquido. Si\neste Pokémon se enfriara, el magma perdería el calor y se\nsolidificaría, por lo que se resquebrajaría por completo,\nperdería algunos trozos y reduciría su tamaño.",
      "language": {
        "name": "es",
        "url": "json/language/0007.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "omega-ruby",
        "url": "json/version/0025.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Durch Schneckmags Kreislaufsystem fließt Magma.\nWenn dieses Pokémon erkältet ist, kühlt das Magma\naus und erhärtet. Sein Körper wird spröde und es\nbrechen Stücke heraus, sodass es kleiner wird.",
      "language": {
        "name": "de",
        "url": "json/language/0006.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "omega-ruby",
        "url": "json/version/0025.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Du magma en fusion coule dans les veines de Limagma.\nSi ce Pokémon est refroidi, le magma se solidifie. Son corps\ndevient alors cassant et des morceaux s’en détachent,\ndiminuant ainsi sa taille.",
      "language": {
        "name": "fr",
        "url": "json/language/0005.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "omega-ruby",
        "url": "json/version/0025.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "몸 안에는 작열하는 용암이\n소용돌이치지만 식으면 굳어지고\n부서져서 몸이 작아진다.",
      "language": {
        "name": "ko",
        "url": "json/language/0003.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "omega-ruby",
        "url": "json/version/0025.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "からだの　なかでは　しゃくねつの　ようがんが\nうずまいているが　ひえると　かたまって　しまい\nくずれて　からだが　ちいさく　なっていく。",
      "language": {
        "name": "ja-Hrkt",
        "url": "json/language/0001.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "omega-ruby",
        "url": "json/version/0025.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "溶岩で　できた　体を　持つ。\n絶えず　動いていないと　体が\n冷えて　固まってしまうのだ。",
      "language": {
        "name": "ja",
        "url": "json/language/0011.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "y",
        "url": "json/version/0024.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Its body is made of magma. If it doesn’t keep\nmoving, its body will cool and harden.",
      "language": {
        "name": "en",
        "url": "json/language/0009.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "y",
        "url": "json/version/0024.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Nel suo corpo scorre magma. Se non si muove\ncontinuamente, il suo corpo si raffredda e s’indurisce.",
      "language": {
        "name": "it",
        "url": "json/language/0008.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "y",
        "url": "json/version/0024.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Su cuerpo se compone de magma. Si deja de\nmoverse, se enfría y se endurece.",
      "language": {
        "name": "es",
        "url": "json/language/0007.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "y",
        "url": "json/version/0024.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Sein Körper besteht aus Magma. Bleibt es nicht\nständig in Bewegung, kühlt es aus und verhärtet sich.",
      "language": {
        "name": "de",
        "url": "json/language/0006.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "y",
        "url": "json/version/0024.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "Son corps est fait de magma. S’il cesse de bouger,\nil refroidit et durcit.",
      "language": {
        "name": "fr",
        "url": "json/language/0005.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "y",
        "url": "json/version/0024.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "용암으로 된 몸을 가지고 있다.\n끊임없이 움직이지 않으면 몸이\n식어 굳어져 버린다.",
      "language": {
        "name": "ko",
        "url": "json/language/0003.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "y",
        "url": "json/version/0024.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "ようがんで　できた　からだを　もつ。\nたえず　うごいていないと　からだが\nひえて　かたまってしまうのだ。",
      "language": {
        "name": "ja-Hrkt",
        "url": "json/language/0001.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "y",
        "url": "json/version/0024.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "火山地帯に　多く　発生。\n暖かい　ところを　探して\nのろのろ　はいずり回っている。",
      "language": {
        "name": "ja",
        "url": "json/language/0011.json"
      },
      "version": {
        "name": "x",
        "url": "json/version/0023.json"
      }
    },
    {
      "flavor_text": "A common sight in volcanic areas, it slowly slithers\naround in a constant search for warm places.",
